  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Corruption\nRisk Mapping – Interview Report</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Introductory\nInformation</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Item </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Content </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Interview Date </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  border-right:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-left-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12\n  February 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Interviewee </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  border-right:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-left-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Thomas\n  Böhm<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Position </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  border-right:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-left-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Finance\n  Director – Europlasma Group<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black;mso-ansi-language:\n  EN-US\">Interviewers </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  border-right:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;\n  mso-border-left-alt:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Antoine\n  Lassauge, Sandra Lezmi<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi\"><br>\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\n<!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1. Scope\nof Responsibilities and Activities</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Department\n&amp; Role:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Finance Director of the\n     Europlasma Group.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Supervision of finance for\n     plasma collection activities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Management of financial\n     operations in <b>thre</b>e countries : Austria , Germany , Czech Republic\n     (two entities: Europlasma s.r.o and Amber Plasma s.r.o).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Steering the\n     professionalisation of group-level financial processes, notably in the\n     context of integrating Amber Plasma.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Team\n&amp; Organisation:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Local finance teams (including\n     a team inherited from Amber Plasma in the Czech Republic)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo2;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Significant use of external\n     service providers: accounting, payroll, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Relevant\nOperational Processes:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Procurement / Purchasing</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (purchase requests via PRF).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Financial Controls</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (PO validation, supplier validation, invoice analysis).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Payments</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (outsourced to accounting service providers).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Cash Management</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> in donation centres (donor payouts and minor expenses).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Post‑acquisition Integration</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (systems, procedures, controls).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Investment Management</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (construction of centres, equipment).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Systems\nUsed:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Different local solutions from\n     one country to another<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. Third\nParties, Interactions, Risks and Controls</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Types of\nThird Parties:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Strategic International\n     Suppliers</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo5;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">E.g.: <i>Haemonetics</i>\n      (plasmapheresis machines).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level2 lfo5;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Relations managed by the\n      Europlasma CEO &amp; LFB Corporate.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">External Service Providers<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Marketing / Sponsorship\n     Partners<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:53.4pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\n115%;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 53.4pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Local sports clubs (e.g.: Handball\nin Austria).</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:53.4pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\n115%;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo6;tab-stops:list 53.4pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Local marketing agencies.<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo5;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Plasma Donors<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:53.4pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 53.4pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\nfont-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Receive financial compensation\n(mainly in cash).</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. Points\nRaised by the Interviewee and Associated Controls</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Effort to improve the professionalization\n     of finance activities and gradual integration of systems in the Czech\n     Republic , temporarily creating less-controlled areas.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Controls in place:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Verification of bank details\n     and IBAN</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> for new suppliers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Systematic invoice analysis</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> : consistency, breakdown, contract compliance.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Segregation of duties</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> :<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Operations → receipt / service\n      delivered.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Finance → control and\n      validation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">External accountants → payment\n      preparation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">PRF mandatory above €6K </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">but in practice, this threshold is often not respected; above,\n     hierarchical approval matrix<b> <o:p></o:p></b></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Enhanced controls for\n     construction projects (high capex).<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Accounting and payroll\n     outsourced (reducing internal risk).<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Potential\nissues:<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Excessive reliance on certain\n     suppliers </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">→ operational and financial risk -&gt; Issue of\n     supplier diversification and competition<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Competition implemented without\n     clearly defined thresholds or systematic integration of the finance\n     department – absence of a purchasing department<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo8;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Regarding donor compensation:\n     In cash<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Daily cash register statements\n      + reconciliation (donors × amounts paid).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Limiting cash amounts in\n      centres (frequent orders).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo8;\n      tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Despite a cashless pilot, need\n      to compensate donors in cash – Amount can reach up to €60K/month for the\n      largest centre (with replenishment every week)<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:115%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">TBC: Existence\nor absence of purchasing procedures + third party evaluation</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">@Confirmer l’existence ou non de procédures achats +\névaluation des tiers<o:p></o:p></p>",
